        {
            "title": "港股午後初段跌幅收窄 科指暫轉升 免稅概念炒上",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股午後持續向好，對港股氣氛提供支持。恒生指數午後初段跌幅曾收窄至67點，重越二萬關，高見20060點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國中免官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241030_FI_source-web_01880-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國中免官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241030_FI_source-web_01880-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國中免官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至下午約2時09分，恒指跌101點，報20025點；恒生科技指數早前已轉升，暫報4620點，升52點或1.15%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">免稅概念股於內地A股市場大幅炒上，中國中免(01880)A股(601888.SH)漲停板，該公司在港股價亦高踞不下，最高曾見54.5元，飆18.87%；暫報52.95元，仍升15.49%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14841494-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84-%e7%a7%91%e6%8c%87%e6%9a%ab%e8%bd%89%e5%8d%87-%e5%85%8d%e7%a8%85%e6%a6%82%e5%bf%b5%e7%82%92%e4%b8%8a",
